{"tid":593383,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺香港都唔少肥妹只要肯減肥都係女神級","createTime":"2018-03-15T02:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T04:48:19.000Z","uid":4349,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d0d9a1938d655808e033a84e49e62c66f38c7e","tid":593383,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"識幾個肥妹(唔係微胖係真係肥果隻)，五官其實好靚<br />\n呢班肥妹多數都唔係由細至大肥開，係大個唔知受咩刺激暴肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中一個肥妹，睇佢以前d相，屌奶星成個iu咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢做乜唔做運動減肥，實變番女神，佢一句話懶同中意食就end左topic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難怪既，香港地靚肥婆都實有人追，吹佢地唔漲，不過堆埋身既男仔都唔會太高質就一定<br />\n睇番呢班肥妹都有共同點，就係對自我要求太低，對自己無乜要求，對男朋友條件都無乜要求<br />\n肯減肥既話，男神都仆住咁湧埋黎啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw係講緊肥妹，即係23樓下果堆，佢地仲有翻身既潛力<br />\n24/25打上果堆肥婆就算撚數啦，你地由身至心到dna,連靈魂都已經比肥膏侵蝕敗壞哂，整容抽脂都唔會整得走侵肥西除，你地出番去食肉啦呢到唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad199975b5f5036a53152e83101a96fd693330e","tid":593383,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":39,"score":-36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7835862a1920f795003a641b54a33a28400e27a0","tid":593383,"uid":131259,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"肥C又衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75663b99c2788c2643ca9926fd6a18e0a19453b","tid":593383,"uid":84830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5ad199975b5f5036a53152e83101a96fd693330e","tid":593383,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":39,"score":-36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"嗰個假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bb8833276c106994e8d81553a9f05c610f2d1d","tid":593383,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0